                  "status": "Open",
                  "severity": "Critical",
                  "type": "Elevation of privilege",
                  "description": "A normal user could exploit flaws in session handling or authorization to gain admin access.",
                  "mitigation": "Implement role-based access control (RBAC).\n\nValidate user authorization on every request.\n\nRegularly test for privilege escalation vulnerabilities.",
